name: gst_plugins_good
deps: gst_plugins_base, cairo, flac, lame, mpg123, mesa, gdk_pixbuf, libgudev, libjpeg_turbo, libpng, libsoup, libvpx, xorg_libraries, aalib, gtk3, libdv, pulseaudio, speex, taglib, v4l_utils
desc:
The GStreamer Good Plug-ins is a set of plug-ins considered by 
the GStreamer developers to have good quality code, correct 
functionality, and the preferred license 
(LGPL for the plug-in code, LGPL or LGPL-compatible 
for the supporting library). A wide range of video and audio decoders, 
encoders, and filters are included.
